title: Teenager missing from Downpatrick area | UTV - ITV News
text:
15 February 2017 at 7:32am Teenager missing from Downpatrick area 
Police in Downpatrick are becoming increasingly concerned for the welfare of a missing 14-year-old girl. 
Katie Lilburn was last seen in the Bangor area on Saturday 11 February. 
Katie is described as being around 5’4” tall, of slim build with long blonde hair with dyed red tips and was wearing light grey jeans, a navy and white tracksuit top and white trainers. 
Inspector Philip Quinn has appealed to Katie or anyone who knows of her whereabouts to contact officers in Downpatrick on 101 quoting reference number 974 11/02/17. Last updated Wed 15 Feb 2017
